headline: BIIB Q1 Earnings Call: New Product Growth Outpaces Declining MS Franchise Amid Lowered Guidance
summary: Biotech company Biogen (NASDAQ:BIIB) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 6.1% year on year to $2.43 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.02 per share was 1.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
